Package: giftwrapr
Type: Package
Title: Generate Dockerfiles for R Projects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("John", "Flournoy", email = "john-flournoy@pluralsight.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1735-1221")))
Description: The giftwrapr package helps users to generate Dockerfiles for R projects based on the rocker-verse images. It detects the R packages used in the project directory, creates a Dockerfile that installs those packages, and optionally builds the Docker image locally or triggers a remote build.
